items.sentence: I hope that we can come up with a better plan.
Tom and his friends threw Mary into the water.
The police think Tom fell asleep at the wheel.
Tom dropped his empty gun and started running.
This crowd reminds me of the streets of Tokyo.
I don't believe the child came to Tokyo alone.
They had lived there until they came to Tokyo.
I never dreamed that there would be a typhoon.
Tom has kept his feelings for Mary to himself.
I don't think doing it that way would be fair.
